data.description: $5000 SELLER CONTRIBUTION TO BUY DOWN YOUR INTERST RATE!! Gorgeous 1.5 Story 4 Bedroom 3 Full Bath Home on Half an Acre!! You cannot find lots like this at this price point anymore. Located just off Loop 1604, with easy access to I-35 and I-10. An open Floor Plan with separate dining, formal Living and a family Room with a Fire Place. Spacious island kitchen has Silestone countertops, stainless appliances and 42" upper cabinets. Large master bedroom has a custom walk-in closet, separate Tub/Shower and a double vanity. Bonus upstairs with a gameroom, bedroom and full bath. Huge fenced backyard with an afternoon shaded covered patio and storage shed. Close shopping and restaurants.
